    "Body": " TRON is dedicated to build the infrastructure for a decentralized Internet. The Tron Protocol, one of the largest blockchain-based operating systems in the world, offers scalable, high-availability, and high-throughput platform that serves as the foundation for all decentralized applications in the TRON ecosystem. We are seeking a few Senior Founding Members to build our P2P Streaming Platform. You will join the core live streaming team, retool the existing p2p live protocol/algorithm to build a decentralized live streaming product. As the Founding Member for our live streaming team, you will... Build the decentralized peer to peer live streaming protocol Participate in the design and implementation of performant and resilient distributed applications Create or maintain software libraries and programs depended on by other systems and applications Work alongside a cross-functional team including engineering, design, product, and business What You May Gain Working Here... Integration of blockchain technologies into applications BitTorrent protocol, at least the basics Scaling an application for use by 100 million users More than what you already know You may be a fit for this role if you have... Experience programming in C++11 Deep understanding of network protocols (HTTP, TCP, UDP, HTTPS/SSL, DHT). BitTorrent protocol is desirable. Experience with streaming protocols RTSP/RTP Experience building peer-to-peer applications It would be fantastic if you know... Familiarity with FFmpeg and transcoding is desirable Be able to use at least one well-supported scripting language in developing test programs. Be comfortable with a rapid-iteration style of software development. Excellent written and verbal communication skills Experience building mobile applications (Android and/or iOS) is desirable. What We Offer Competitive salary and 401K. 100% paid health coverage (for you and your family) that includes dental and vision plans. Flexible working hours, including the ability to work from home (on occasion or as needed) Unlimited paid time off Plenty of free food at the office, 4 rotating kegs on tap, and yummy catered lunches. Regular team-wide outdoor events and parties. Up to $50/month wellness benefit at a gym or wellness group of your choice Your choice of the latest, top-of-the-line equipment and tools to work with. Work with heaps of smart, awesome people, including a surprising number of people who are great at pool, pinball, and foosball. TRON-BitTorrent is an equal opportunity employer and values diversity at our company. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, religion, color, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, veteran status or disability status. ", 
